==發行==
===票房===
在香港院線上映期間，《春光乍洩》的票房收入為8,600,141港幣。<ref>{{Cite web|title=1997 香港票房 {{!}} 中国电影票房榜|url=http://www.boxofficecn.com/hkboxoffice1997|access-date=2022-01-01|language=zh-CN|archive-date=2022-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220101053751/http://www.boxofficecn.com/hkboxoffice1997}}</ref>《春光乍洩》還通過奇諾國際公司在北美進行了有限的影院放映，票房收入為320,319美元。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=happytogether.htm|title=Happy Together (1997) - Box Office Mojo|website=boxofficemojo.com|language=en|access-date=2018-04-02|archive-date=2018-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180402101921/http://www.boxofficemojo.com/movies/?id=happytogether.htm}}</ref>
===多媒體===
奇諾國際公司於2010年6月8日發行了這部電影的DVD和藍光光盤。該版本現已絕版。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Happy-Together-Blu-ray/9448/|title=Happy Together Blu-ray (春光乍洩 / Chun gwong cha sit)|access-date=2022-02-22|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422062441/https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/Happy-Together-Blu-ray/9448/}}</ref>這部電影後被[[標準收藏版公司|標準收藏]]收錄，並於2021年3月23日與其他七部王家衛電影發行藍光版本。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/World-of-Wong-Kar-Wai-Blu-ray/261077/|title=World of Wong Kar Wai Blu-ray (DigiPack)|access-date=2022-02-22|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422062441/https://www.blu-ray.com/movies/World-of-Wong-Kar-Wai-Blu-ray/261077/}}</ref>
===評論===
《春光乍洩》在香港獲得普遍好評，受到[[周蕾|周蕾]]、陳劍梅等眾多中港學者和影評人的深入分析。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.thenewslens.com/article/122303|title=《溫情主義寓言・當代華語電影》：《春光乍洩》愛慾關係轉成深深鄉愁|last=精選書摘|date=2019-07-18|website=The News Lens 關鍵評論網|language=zh-TW|access-date=2020-03-23|archive-date=2022-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422062441/https://www.thenewslens.com/article/122303}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|url=http://www.orangenews.hk/culture/system/2019/10/09/010128429.shtml|title=【黑色電影】《春光乍洩》：身份意識的切換與探索|website=橙新聞|access-date=2020-03-23}}</ref>一家香港影評網站稱其稱為「橢圓的水銀實驗，是純粹的王家衛，渴望、遺憾和悲慘的美並重。」<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.lovehkfilm.com/reviews/happy_together.htm|title=Happy Together (1997)|website=lovehkfilm.com|access-date=2020-03-23|archive-date=2022-02-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220222100625/https://www.lovehkfilm.com/reviews/happy_together.htm}}</ref>
由於《春光乍洩》獲得了國際認可，它在美國幾家主要出版社上發布了相關評論。《舊金山紀事報》的愛德華·古斯曼（Edward Guthmann）對這部電影進行欣喜若狂的評論，對杜可風的創新攝影和導演手法大加讚賞<ref>{{cite web |author=Edward Guthmann |url=http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=/c/a/1997/11/14/DD24951.DTL |title=Misery Loves Company in 'Happy Together' |work=San Francisco Chronicle |date=14 November 1997 |access-date=20 January 2012 |archive-date=2011-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110524211400/http://www.sfgate.com/cgi-bin/article.cgi?f=%2Fc%2Fa%2F1997%2F11%2F14%2FDD24951.DTL }}</ref>；《紐約時報》的斯蒂芬·霍爾頓表示，這是一部比王家衛以前的電影還更加連貫、更發自於內心的電影，同時又不失他早期作品的魯莽風格。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://movies2.nytimes.com/mem/movies/review.html?title1=&title2=Happy%20Together%20%28Movie%29%20%20&reviewer=Stephen%20Holden&v_id=155000&partner=Rotten%20Tomatoes |title=Help – The New York Times |publisher=Movies2.nytimes.com |access-date=20 January 2012 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151017025727/http://movies2.nytimes.com/mem/movies/review.html?title1=&title2=Happy%20Together%20%28Movie%29%20%20&reviewer=Stephen%20Holden&v_id=155000&partner=Rotten%20Tomatoes |archive-date=17 October 2015 |url-status=dead }}</ref>《綜藝》的德里克·埃利（Derek Elley）給出了總體正面的評價，稱其為王家衛在一段時間以來最感性和最成熟的作品，埃利也稱讚了電影場景佈置、音樂和[[張叔平|張叔平]]的美術設計。他強調杜可風是這部電影「真正的明星」，因為其在畫面所造的高對比度攝影技術，亞洲電影脈搏一方則表示，張國榮和梁朝偉都是電影中的主角。<ref name=":3">{{Cite web|url=https://asianmoviepulse.com/2019/08/film-review-happy-together-1997-by-wong-kar-wai/|title=Film Review: Happy Together (1997) by Wong Kar-wai|last=Thayne|first=Andrew|date=2019-08-28|website=Asian Movie Pulse|language=en-US|access-date=2020-03-23|archive-date=2021-04-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210429093744/https://asianmoviepulse.com/2019/08/film-review-happy-together-1997-by-wong-kar-wai/}}</ref>

然而，喬納森·羅森鮑姆在《芝加哥讀者雜誌》上對這部電影的評價褒貶不一<ref>{{cite web |last=Champlin |first=Craig |url=http://www.chicagoreader.com/movies/archives/1998/0198/01238.html |title=Music, movies, news, culture & food |publisher=Chicago Reader |access-date=20 January 2012 |archive-date=2009-07-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090714132723/http://www.chicagoreader.com/movies/archives/1998/0198/01238.html }}</ref>。對於電影的總結中批評其情節模糊。在《票房雜誌》中，韋德梅傑給了這部電影最負面的評價之一，稱它“在風格或敘事上幾乎沒有進步，儘管它應該是取悅他的核心粉絲”。他不贊成王家衛的攝影稱其為“隨機實驗”，表示由於缺乏敘事性，電影“令人難以忍受的乏味”。<ref>{{cite web |author=Sparktech Software LLC |url=http://boxoffice.com/reviews/2008/08/happy-together.php |title=Happy Together – Inside Movies Since 1920 |publisher=Boxoffice.com |date=10 October 1997 |access-date=20 January 2012 |url-status=dead |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100205153827/http://boxoffice.com/reviews/2008/08/happy-together.php |archive-date=5 February 2010}}</ref>
在[[爛番茄|爛番茄]]上，根據38條評論，這部電影的支持率為82%，平均評分為7.30/10。該網站的評論共識是：即使敘事乏味，但《春光乍洩》強烈的風格性與其生活中的愛情故事反倒相得益彰。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1083093-happy_together |title=Happy Together (Chun gwong cha sit) (1997) |website=[[Rotten_Tomatoes|Rotten Tomatoes]] |publisher=[[Fandango_Media|Fandango]] |access-date=27 March 2021 |archive-date=2022-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623120243/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/1083093-happy_together }}</ref>[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]則根據17條評論，這部電影的加權平均得分為70分（滿分100分），獲得「普遍好評」的分數。<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.metacritic.com/movie/happy-together |title=Happy Together Reviews |publisher=[[Metacritic|Metacritic]] |access-date=22 September 2020 |archive-date=2022-05-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220503135632/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/happy-together }}</ref>

